                     <interp inst="t18501216-235-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing five yards of carpet, value 25<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18501216-name-221" type="victimName">
